org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable

Interface MobSpawnerData.NextEntityToSpawnValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<WeightedEntity>, Value<WeightedEntity>
    Enclosing interface:
    MobSpawnerData

    public static interface MobSpawnerData.NextEntityToSpawnValue
extends Value<WeightedEntity>
    Represents a custom Value dealing with the next WeightedEntity such that the next Entity to spawn may be pulled from the owning MobSpawnerData.possibleEntitiesToSpawn() with a default Random, or it may be custom defined on a case by case basis.
